# ONE-CELL NOTEBOOK: summarize all .msg conversations into DOCX + HTML + PDF (<= ~2500 words)
# - Reads .msg from your 3 folders (Mails, Mails Rasmus, Mails Birgit)
# - Ignores greetings/chatter, extracts real Q/A + requirements + decisions
# - Uses your Nexus AzureOpenAI (gpt-5.1) via OPENAI_API_KEY env var
# - Writes outputs into: ...\Available data\new data\mail_summaries\
#
# Prereqs:
#   py -m pip install --user openai extract-msg python-docx reportlab
#   (You already have openai; reportlab/docx might already be installed now.)

